    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from its original showroom state, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
