      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out. I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream! If you're looking for absolute perfection, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
