    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Double-VANOS overhaul to ensure peak valvetrain timing. The chassis is verified for structural integrity with a reinforced rear subframe. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the car retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and M-variable limited-slip differential. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
