    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-fresh appearance. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and every tactile surface\u2014from the steering wheel to the switchgear\u2014feels as crisp as the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-verified service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists using OEM parts. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every component reflects a 'no-expense-spared' ownership philosophy. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle, offering a flawless, rattle-free experience for the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
