      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute stunner. It is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without that dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come fall in love with your new car!",
