    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54 platform, maintained with surgical precision. The 3.2L atmospheric straight-six delivers linear power through a 6-speed Getrag manual, with the VANOS system recently overhauled for peak cam phasing. The chassis has been comprehensively addressed, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein dampers. The exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible stone chips or oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. Recent leak-down and compression tests confirm exceptional internal health across all cylinders. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key masterpiece for the collector who prioritizes engineering integrity and visceral performance.",
